887.83.text:
In the Book of Isaiah, God says - 
&quot;O Israel, fear not, for I will redeem you, 
and I love you.&quot;

1502.50.text:
but, he writes - 
&quot;We came from love. 
We are created in love.&quot;

1790.01.text:
